Name:                scons2dot
Version:             0.9
Synopsis:            Generates graphviz file of scons dependency information
Description:         This tool creates a graphviz dot file that represents
                     build dependencies on a system built with scons.
License:             GPL
License-file:        COPYING
Author:              Leandro Lisboa Penz
Maintainer:          Leandro Lisboa Penz <llpenz@gmail.com>
Build-type:          Simple
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.6
Category:            Development
Extra-source-files:  manual.t2t

Executable           scons2dot
  Main-is:           scons2dot.hs
  Build-depends:     base >= 3 && < 4,bytestring,containers,process

Source-repository    head
  Type:              git
  Location:          git://github.com/lpenz/scons2dot.git

